==Channel vision== Alryyan TV adopts Qatar National Vision (2030) and aspires to be a supportive media for achieving sustainable development through three main functions: "Development, Awareness and [[Entertainment]]", which the [[Television channel|channel]] will translate into a program mix representing its media strategy. Al Rayyan is a diverse channel that targets the [[Qatar]]i community as a key audience and takes into account the specificity of its national identity and aspirations. It aims at promoting the development of the society and educating its groups to contribute to the realization of the [[Qatar]] National Vision (2030). It also promotes the values of virtue and positiveness, the authenticity of the [[Qatar]]i heritage, the support of [[social]] communication and the promotion of the spirit of competition and creative thinking among the youth in general and all segments of society in general. Useful and within the framework of combining interest and [[entertainment]] using the best production and [[broadcast]] techniques. The channel will also keep abreast of the times by announcing a visionary creed that supports the renaissance of [[Qatar]] and contributes to sustainable development.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://alarab.qa/story/1211702/%D8%B5%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AD-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%85%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A7-%D9%84%D9%82%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%81%D8%B6%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%8A%D8%A9|title=العرب القطرية: صباح الكواري مديراً لقناة الريان الفضائية|website=العرب القطرية|accessdate=23 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.al-sharq.com/news/details/398139|title=قناة الريان الفضائية تطلق قناتها الثانية - الشرق|website=Al-sharq.com|accessdate=23 August 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelsfrequency.com/%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%AF-%D9%82%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AC%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%AF-20162017-alrayyan-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%86%