| result      = Algerian victory{{sfn|Emerit|2010|pp=18–19}}
| combatant1  = {{flagicon|France}} [[July Monarchy|France]]
| combatant2  = [[File:Dz flag-Abdelkader.png|23px]] [[Emirate of Abdelkader|Algerian resistance]]
| commander2  = [[File:Dz flag-Abdelkader.png|23px]] [[Abd al-Qadir al-Jaza'iri]]
| commander1  = [[Camille Alphonse Trézel]]
