{{Infobox flag
|Name= Sindh province
|Image=Flag of Sindh.svg
|Use=110000
|Symbol=[[File:IFIS De facto.svg]] [[File:IFIS Vertical inapplicable.svg]]
|Proportion=2:3|Adoption=23 May 2005
