{{Infobox Union |name= CSB |country= [[Burkina Faso]] |affiliation= [[International Trade Union Confederation|ITUC]] |members= |full_name= Trade Union Confederation of Burkina |native_name= Confédération Syndicale Burkinabé |image= |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Ouagadougou]], Burkina Faso |people= [[Jean-Mathias Liliou]], secretary general |website= |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Trade Union Confederation of Burkina''' (CSB) is a [[trade union]] centre in [[Burkina Faso]]. It is affiliated with the [[International Trade Union Confederation]].
